title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 5/16 - Micheletti/Vikings Rookie Camp
description: PA opens the show talking about what he saw from Lewis Cine & Brian Asamoah at Vikings rookie camp, the conversation switches to Mavs/Suns Game 7 & the ascension of Luka Doncic, plus Pat Micheletti calls in to discuss what happened to the Wild in their series with St. Louis.
